パッケージ com.astamuse.asta4d.data

  • インタフェースの概要 
    インタフェース 説明
    ContextDataFinder
    This interface declares how to find a certain data in Context.
    DataConvertor<S,T>
    This interface is used by InjectUtil to convert context data to the appropriate type automatically
  • クラスの概要 
    クラス 説明
    ArrayDataConvertor<S,T>  
    ContextBindData<T>
    a ContextBindData is supposed to be cache in the current thread Context and should only be initialized once
    ContextDataHolder<T>  
    DefaultContextDataFinder
    A default implementation of ContextDataFinder.
    InjectUtil
    This class is a function holder to supply functionalities about data injection
  • 例外の概要 
    例外 説明
    DataOperationException
    A DataOperationException is thrown when error occurs in injection process.
